name: Shoe-Store.net
overview: The people who own Oppedisano’s Shoe Store will often be the same ones who answer your phone calls and e-mail inquiries. We believe that direct owner involvement in the day-to-day operations is the only way to operate a successful business. Our personalized service means you don’t have to wait on hold or receive second tier service or substandard knowledge from a customer service department. So, feel free to contact us anytime. We are quite sure you’ll be happy with the service you receive.
